m actual child porn videos. To prevent any malware or cyberfraud-related troubles when it comes to adult content , Kaspersky Lab advised users to follow these recommendations:- Use only trusted websites when it comes to adult content. Cybercriminals often set up fake porn sites for the single purpose of infecting victims with malware.- Do not install Android applications from unknown sources, even if they promise you access to the content you were looking for. Instead, use official applications from official sources, like Google Play.- Avoid purchasing hacked accounts to porn websites. This is illegal and such accounts may be blocked by the time you purchase it.- Use reliable internet security solution capable of protecting all your devices from any kind of cyberthreats.